Class clRequestMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.androidtown.sleeper.propclasses.com_manager.clMessage
      • org.androidtown.sleeper.propclasses.com_manager.clRequestMessage

  • public class clRequestMessage
extends clMessage
    Make, dissolve request message to/from remote device. Currently, there is no use of dissolving request message since request message is always made and sent from app side and ap device only work as server. But for future modification, we remain code for dissolving.
